  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/89e5f7b3a877604c638a4e916696af4f.poster.avif?t=1750436088\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/89e5f7b3a877604c638a4e916696af4f.webm?t=1750436088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/89e5f7b3a877604c638a4e916696af4f.mp4?t=1750436088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Blast your way through hell in Shotgun Cop Man</strong>, a precision platformer where your weapons are your wings.<br><br>Embark on a mission to arrest Satan armed with a devastating arsenal and a relentless thirst for glory. Propel yourself through hordes of irritable demons, devious traps, and thrilling challenges using the only two things you can trust: your wits and your weapons.<br><br>Conquer the handcrafted campaign or dive into user-generated levels in this fire and brimstone-fueled mission to serve justice.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/b2efe11a37670a6f32ac663d47948045.poster.avif?t=1750436088\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/b2efe11a37670a6f32ac663d47948045.webm?t=1750436088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/b2efe11a37670a6f32ac663d47948045.mp4?t=1750436088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Firepower Propulsion</h2>Master your movement through the twisted corners of hell as every shot propels you forward. Whether dodging enemies, scaling walls, or leaping impossible gaps, your weapons are the key to both survival and traversal.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explosive Campaign and Challenges</h2>Dive into an action-packed campaign in over 150 levels and face off against intense boss battles, then put yourself to the test and beat all the No Damage, Speedrun, and Kill All challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/6780e4d90a5acc472a2655da1f97ef87.poster.avif?t=1750436088\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/6780e4d90a5acc472a2655da1f97ef87.webm?t=1750436088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/6780e4d90a5acc472a2655da1f97ef87.mp4?t=1750436088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create Your Own Hellish Playground</h2>Let your creativity shine with the built-in level editor and Steam Workshop integration. Craft, share, and conquer custom levels to push the game and your peers to their limits.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/89e5f7b3a877604c638a4e916696af4f.poster.avif?t=1750436088\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/89e5f7b3a877604c638a4e916696af4f.webm?t=1750436088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/89e5f7b3a877604c638a4e916696af4f.mp4?t=1750436088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Blast your way through hell in Shotgun Cop Man</strong>, a precision platformer where your weapons are your wings.<br><br>Embark on a mission to arrest Satan armed with a devastating arsenal and a relentless thirst for glory. Propel yourself through hordes of irritable demons, devious traps, and thrilling challenges using the only two things you can trust: your wits and your weapons.<br><br>Conquer the handcrafted campaign or dive into user-generated levels in this fire and brimstone-fueled mission to serve justice.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/b2efe11a37670a6f32ac663d47948045.poster.avif?t=1750436088\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/b2efe11a37670a6f32ac663d47948045.webm?t=1750436088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/b2efe11a37670a6f32ac663d47948045.mp4?t=1750436088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Firepower Propulsion</h2>Master your movement through the twisted corners of hell as every shot propels you forward. Whether dodging enemies, scaling walls, or leaping impossible gaps, your weapons are the key to both survival and traversal.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explosive Campaign and Challenges</h2>Dive into an action-packed campaign in over 150 levels and face off against intense boss battles, then put yourself to the test and beat all the No Damage, Speedrun, and Kill All challenges.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/6780e4d90a5acc472a2655da1f97ef87.poster.avif?t=1750436088\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/6780e4d90a5acc472a2655da1f97ef87.webm?t=1750436088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966850/extras/6780e4d90a5acc472a2655da1f97ef87.mp4?t=1750436088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create Your Own Hellish Playground</h2>Let your creativity shine with the built-in level editor and Steam Workshop integration. Craft, share, and conquer custom levels to push the game and your peers to their limits.",
